name: Oi na praca sé que a policia me parou
lyrics:
oi na praca sé que a policia me parou
No meio da confusao a policia me pegou
Pára pára pára, pára seu doctor

translations.text:
Hi, in the square, I know the police stopped me.
In the middle of the confusion the police got me
Stop to stop, stop your doctor
